Veggie Pinto Beet Bean Burger
  --America's Test Kitchen

2/3 bulgar (medium) rinsed
1/2 tsp salt
1 1/2 c boiling water

Put all together in a pot, let stand for 20 min to hydrate

3/4 c vegan mayo
2 tbsp shoyu
1 tbsp vegan worcestershire
1 tbsp brown sugar
1 garlic clove minced
1 tbsp fresh chives
3/4 tsp pepper

whisk together 

Drain bulgar, spread out on sheetpan to cool down

1 large beet grated
3/4 c walnuts
1/2 c fresh basil
2 garlic cloves

place in food processor, pulse 12 times

1 can pinto beans, rinsed and drained
1 c carrot baby food
1 tbsp grainy mustard
2 tbsp water
1 1/2 tsp salt
1/2 tsp pepper

add to food processor, pulse 8 times, pour into a bowl

1 1/2 c panko bread crumbs

Add bread crumbs, bulgar, and contents of food processor and combine. Form into 8 patties, 3 1/2" diameter.
Cook 4 at a time for 4 min on each side in skillet with oil, add more oil as needed.
